"策略路由表的起始编号。每个已选择且配置了出口接口的 NaiveProxy 节点使用该值加"
"上其节点序号。"

#: htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/bypass/basic_settings.js:228
msgid "Egress rule priority"
msgstr "出口规则优先级"

#: htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/bypass/basic_settings.js:229
msgid ""
"Base priority of the per-node destination policy rules. The default 900 runs "
"before Passwall2/mwan3-style marked rules without modifying their packet "
"marks."
msgstr ""
"节点目标策略规则的起始优先级。默认值 900 会先于 Passwall2/mwan3 风格的标记规"
"则执行，且不会修改其数据包标记。"

#: htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/bypass/basic_settings.js:234
msgid "Start Delay (seconds)"
msgstr "启动延迟（秒）"

#: htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/bypass/basic_settings.js:235
