"AsIs = no DNS resolution. IpIfNonMatch = resolve on domain mismatch. "
"IpOnDemand = resolve when a rule needs an IP."
msgstr ""
"AsIs = 不解析 DNS；IpIfNonMatch = 域名未命中时解析；IpOnDemand = 规则需要 IP "
"时解析。"

#: htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/bypass/basic_settings.js:250
msgid "Domain matcher"
msgstr "域名匹配器"

msgid "BypassCore 1.0.5 uses its optimized Linux domain matcher. Hybrid is the only compatible value; Xray's linear matcher does not exist in BypassCore."
msgstr "BypassCore 1.0.5 使用其针对 Linux 优化的域名匹配器。Hybrid 是唯一兼容值；BypassCore 中不存在 Xray 的 linear 匹配器。"

#: htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/bypass/basic_settings.js:251
msgid "hybrid"
msgstr "混合"

#: htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/bypass/basic_settings.js:256
msgid "Direct DNS result write to NFTSet"
msgstr "直连 DNS 结果写入 NFTSet"

#: htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/bypass/basic_settings.js:257
msgid ""
"Write addresses resolved for matching direct-domain rules to an informational "
"NFTSet. BypassCore still makes every ordered traffic decision because "
"unrelated hostnames can share an IP address."
msgstr ""
"将命中直连域名规则所解析出的地址写入信息用途的 NFTSet。由于不同域名可能共享同"
"一个 IP 地址，所有有序流量决策仍由 BypassCore 完成。"

#: htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/bypass/basic_settings.js:262
msgid "Enable GeoIP Data Parsing"
msgstr "启用 GeoIP 数据解析"

#: htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/bypass/basic_settings.js:263
msgid ""
"Parse Direct-rule GeoIP entries into an informational NFTSet for diagnostics "
"and compatibility. BypassCore always remains responsible for ordered routing "
"decisions."
msgstr ""
"将直连规则中的 GeoIP 条目解析到信息用途的 NFTSet，供诊断和兼容使用；有序路由决"
"策始终由 BypassCore 负责。"

