msgstr "直连查询策略"

#: htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/bypass/basic_settings.js:326
msgid "Remote DNS Protocol"
msgstr "国外 DNS 协议"

#: htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/bypass/basic_settings.js:327
msgid ""
"BypassCore carries TCP, TLS (DoT), and DoH through the selected NaiveProxy "
"node. UDP requires Direct outbound because NaiveProxy has no UDP transport."
msgstr ""
"BypassCore 可通过所选 NaiveProxy 节点承载 TCP、TLS（DoT）和 DoH。由于 "
"NaiveProxy 不支持 UDP，UDP 必须选择直连出站。"

