msgid "Remote DNS DoH"
msgstr "国外 DNS DoH"

#: htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/bypass/basic_settings.js:353
msgid "Remote DNS EDNS Client Subnet"
msgstr "国外 DNS EDNS 客户端子网"

#: htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/bypass/basic_settings.js:354
msgid ""
"Tell the DNS server the client location. This must be a public IP and the "
"server must support EDNS Client Subnet (RFC 7871)."
msgstr ""
"向 DNS 服务器告知客户端所在位置。该值必须是公网 IP，且服务器必须支持 EDNS 客"
"户端子网（RFC 7871）。"

