msgid "Remote DNS Outbound"
msgstr "国外 DNS 出站"

msgid ""
"Remote carries TCP, TLS (DoT), or DoH through BypassCore and the selected "
"NaiveProxy node. Direct connects from the router without the proxy."
msgstr "远程会通过 BypassCore 和所选 NaiveProxy 节点承载 TCP、TLS（DoT）或 DoH；直连则由路由器直接连接而不经过代理。"

