#: htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/bypass/basic_settings.js:378
msgid "DNS Redirect"
msgstr "DNS 重定向"

#: htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/bypass/basic_settings.js:379
msgid ""
"Forward dnsmasq to BypassCore DNS and redirect LAN client TCP/UDP port 53 "
"queries to the router, including clients with a hardcoded DNS server. "
"BypassCore applies domain DNS policies and writes DNS results to NFTSets "
"natively."
msgstr ""
"将 dnsmasq 转发到 BypassCore DNS，并把 LAN 客户端的 TCP/UDP 53 端口查询重定向到"
"路由器，包括硬编码了 DNS 服务器的客户端。BypassCore 会原生应用域名 DNS 策略并将"
"解析结果写入 NFTSet。"

